text: LA-32 is a constituency of Azad Kashmir Legislative Assembly which is currently represented by Muhammad Ishaq of Pakistan Muslim League (N). It covers the area of Sialkot Tehsil of Sialkot District in Pakistan. Only refugees from Jammu and Ladakh Settled in Pakistan are eligible to vote. ==Election 2016== elections were held in this constituency on 21 July 2016.
